echo "Redirect assemblies in RemoveOldInsertionPaletteItems Project (.vsproj) File."
::    Arguments
:: 1: Old Project Path
:: 2: New Project Path
:: 3: New TS Version (2014)
:: 4: New TS Utility Version (2014.0.0.0)
:: 5: New TS Interop Version (2014.0.0.0)

